data.eml:eml: A new mawsoniid coelacanth (Actinistia) from the Upper Cretaceous of Southern France

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Lionel Cavin, Xavier Valentin, Géraldine Garcia (2016): A new mawsoniid coelacanth (Actinistia) from the Upper Cretaceous of Southern France. Cretaceous Research 62: 65-73, DOI: 10.1016/j.cretres.2016.02.002
